{"tid":597824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"派糧 越南「比堅尼航空」首開印度直航　網民驚空姐有危險","createTime":"2018-03-19T03:53:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T05:00:12.000Z","uid":72009,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2cb7b158e9bb67171736df681ca39d8194f08f3d","tid":597824,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T03:53:54.000Z","msg":"越南廉航越捷航空公司（VietJet）多次以比堅尼空姐作噱頭吸引眼球，有「比堅尼航空」之稱。越捷航空近日宣布，將會破天荒新增直飛印度的航線。不過，不少網民關心的是「印度強姦案頻生」會令空姐有危險。 <br />\n<br />\n越南與印度的商貿往來開始頻繁，但目前仍沒有直航航班。越捷航空在兩國於新德里舉行的商貿論壇上宣布，將會在今年7至8月開始，新增每周4天來往胡志明巿與新德里的直航航班。 <br />\n<br />\n不少網民關注「比堅尼航空」打入印度市場會衍生風化問題，有人留言稱：「他們知道女人在印度的待遇嗎？印度男子強姦8個月大以至80歲的女性，然後歸咎於她們衣着，我認為航空公司要重新考慮。」但亦有少數網民為印度辯護，指強姦問題亦非如此嚴重。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180319/photo/bknint-20180319000006351-0319_17011_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180319%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180319000006351-0319_17011_001_01p.jpg&h=0a0bbfc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180319/photo/bknint-20180319000006351-0319_17011_001_02p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180319%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180319000006351-0319_17011_001_02p.jpg&h=33868300&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f354c80c9bf56b98532ade02b1699a0956140459","tid":597824,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T03:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b38f4b20133cbf56317f43a844de2d87978910","tid":597824,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T04:06:08.000Z","msg":"上面左一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" c